      • shallGenerateFunctionToEvaluate

        public static boolean shallGenerateFunctionToEvaluate​(SNode expr)
        Arguments for ITemplateCall are expressions we need to evaluate. Simple expressions, like literals or variable references we know how to process, don't require generated function while complex expressions need a java code to get evaluated (unless we implement support for evaluation some day). Simple expressions are to get evaluated with evaluateExpression(SNode)
        Parameters:
        expr - expression to check
        Returns:
        true if expression is not simple enough to get evaluated in runtime without actual Java code generated
